Hey guys! Happy New Year 🥳 I wanna introduce myself: I'm Ponse, 24 years old, Digital Collage Artist from Venezuela 🇻🇪
I am the person behind this account that changed my life forever 🤍

This account was born as a place for artists from all over the world to have a chance to shine, for their work to reach more people.
But along the way, I started to be an artist myself, many things happened and I've been a digital artist since 2021, this is i what I do for a living, it's truly a blessing 🫶✨

So I decided that I'm going to post my art on this account after a long time of inactivity here, I won't repost other artists anymore, my curation work is over and my focus is on my own art career 🫂

I have been posting all my art on @ponse.art but finally decided to also share my stuff here! 💜
Thanks to everyone who has been following all this time, changes are good and I'm ready for this 2024, sending you all my best wishes for this new year ❤️‍🔥
